                    <component>Legacy/Streaming and Messaging</component>
                        <due></due>
                            <votes>0</votes>
                                    <watches>2</watches>
                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="17303189" author="blerer" created="Wed, 17 Mar 2021 08:25:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;While working on &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-16190&quot; title=&quot;Add tests for streaming metrics&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-16190&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-16190&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, I discovered that &lt;tt&gt;StreamingMetrics.ActiveOutboundStreams&lt;/tt&gt; was not used by any part of the code. This appears to be the case since at least &lt;tt&gt;2.1&lt;/tt&gt;. I think it is time that we deprecate it in order to remove it in the future.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17303286" author="blerer" created="Wed, 17 Mar 2021 10:38:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I created a PR to mark the metric as deprecated &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/pull/935&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17303438" author="michaelsembwever" created="Wed, 17 Mar 2021 13:50:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                    </comments>
